title: Treasure Quest Egypt v1.0 [PD]
description:
NEW JEWELS QUEST in EGYTP!!!!!!

A new match-three puzzle game!
Millions of people played on iOS and NOW it is available on you Android!!
Many people love our "Super Jewels Quest". 

And we're very sure you will like "Treasure Quest Egypt". FOR it has following new features:

Real HD graphics. 
9x9 canvas. 
More challenge levels. Total 60 levels for version 1.0 and free update later.
New element: Rock. There some jewels covered by rock that you can not see it's color. You must guess the color and match jewels to destroy it.

This is a MUST-HAVE for anyone who likes jewels game!
"Treasure Quest Egypt" will be the BEST-looking jewel matching game on your android phone and android pad.

We're sure that you're going to love "Treasure Quest Egypt"! Please be sure to rate the game below. Your feedback will help us make the games you love even better.
Good luck and Have FUn!!!!!

What's New:

Initial verstion port from iOS.
Facebook not supported yet.
60+ unique levels.
